    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Afrotrombicula rickenbachi (Taufflieb, 1965), comb. nov., holotype. A, dorsal aspect of idiosoma; B, ventral aspect of idiosoma; C, dorsal idiosomal seta; D, preanal seta. Abbreviations as in Fig. 5. Scale bars: 100 µm (A, B), 20 µm (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8203887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8203889>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Afrotrombicula rickenbachi (Taufflieb, 1965), comb. nov., holotype. A, scutum and eyes; B, dorsal aspect of gnathosoma; C, ventral aspect of gnathosoma; D, leg I, trochanter–tarsus; E, leg II, trochanter–tarsus; F, leg III, trochanter– tarsus. Abbreviations as in Fig. 6. Scale bars: 50 µm (A, D–F), 20 µm (B, C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8203889/files/figure.png" ;
